Package com.wpi.listener

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClearListener
    This part clears the chosen cell on the board.
    CreateGameListener
    This part shows elements on the homeLayout.
    CreateListener
    When press the button create, jump into this part and get the player name and password.
    DownListener
    When press the button down, jump into this part and set the board down.
    ExitListener
    When press the button exit, exit the game.
    JoinGameListener
    When press the button join, jump into this part and show the place for users to input gameID,player name and password.
    JoinListener
    Send the input message to the server.
    LeftListener
    When press the button left, jump into this part and set the board left.
    LockListener
    lock the game.
    MouseMoveListener
    The operation and the function of the operation of the mouse.
    PracticeGameListener
    When press the button practice, practice game layout shows up.
    QuitListener
    Quit the game.
    ResetListener
    When managing user press the button reset, jump into this part and reset the board .
    RightListener
    When press the button right, jump into this part and set the board right.
    SubmitListener
    When press the button submit, jump into this part and submit the word.
    UpListener
    When press the button up, jump into this part and set the board up.
